OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778267471
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats celebrate after
OL,4,Ctaking top target Stockport Council
OL,6,FIn Stockport, no party has managed to
OL,7,Fget the 32 seats needed to get control
OL,8,Fof the council for the last 15 years,
OL,9,Falthough the Lib Dems came closest,
OL,10,Fheading into the elections with 30
OL,11,Fseats.
OL,13,FThe Lib Dem's now have a working
OL,14,Fmajority on Stockport Council, with 33
OL,15,Fcouncillors elected, while Labour lost
OL,16,Ffive councillors.
OL,18,FA party spokesperson said: "This is a
OL,19,Fgreat result and shows that Liberal
OL,20,FDemocrat teams can win right across
OL,21,Fthe country.
OL,26,@zD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
