OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778267471
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats celebrate after
OL,4,Ctaking top target Stockport Council
OL,6,F"Our hardworking local team has held
OL,7,Foff the rise of Reform ` while others
OL,8,Fsought to sow division and chaos, we
OL,9,Ffocused on the issues that matter."
OL,11,FLabour now join the Green Party and
OL,12,FReform UK with two councillors each on
OL,13,FStockport Council.
OL,15,FStockport Council leader Mark Roberts
OL,16,Fsaid: "It's great news for us hear.
OL,17,FIt's a ringing endorsement of the work
OL,18,Fwe do as Liberal Democrats, as local
OL,19,Fchampions that represents the local
OL,20,Fresidents here at Stockport.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
