OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778267471
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats celebrate after
OL,4,Ctaking top target Stockport Council
OL,6,F"We work really well as a team, but
OL,7,Fthat sense of local champion that we
OL,8,Fbring into our politics. We work hard,
OL,9,Fwe deliver for our residents, and our
OL,10,Fresidents have backed us today in
OL,11,Fgiving us this majority."
OL,13,FHe said he believes the Lib Dems are
OL,14,Fthe party to beat Reform, who won two
OL,15,Fseats in Stockport- the regions first
OL,16,FReform councillors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
