OL,3,CLiberal Democrats celebrate after
OL,4,Ctaking top target Stockport Council
OL,6,FBrian Battle, who won for Reform in
OL,7,Fthe Manor Ward, said: "There's been so
OL,8,Fmuch work that has gone into this, I'm
OL,9,Fjust disappointed some of my
OL,10,Fcolleagues didn't get into it."
OL,12,FHe said he thinks the party performed
OL,13,Fwell in the region, despite only
OL,14,Fwinning two out of 21 seats available.
OL,16,FCouncillor Christine Carrigan, leader
OL,17,Fof Stockport Labour group, said she
OL,18,Fwas 'really disappointed' with the
OL,19,Flocal election results.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
