OL,3,CLiberal Democrats celebrate after
OL,4,Ctaking top target Stockport Council
OL,6,FShe told the Local Democracy Reporting
OL,7,FService: "We now know where we stand
OL,8,Ffor next year, and we absolutely
OL,9,Fintend to make this fight all the way
OL,10,Fback to 2027."
OL,12,FAsked why voters didn't back Labour in
OL,13,FStockport this year, Councillor
OL,14,FCarrigan added: "I can't answer that
OL,15,Fquestion, I think people will
OL,16,Fabsolutely draw their own conclusions.
OL,26,@oD@JOUrD@NO]vD@QOU
