OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778267471
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats celebrate after
OL,4,Ctaking top target Stockport Council
OL,6,F"I know over the next couple of days
OL,7,Fthere will be lots of discussions
OL,8,Fabout that, I have my own opinions,
OL,9,Fand we as a Labour group will come
OL,10,Ftogether in the coming days and have a
OL,11,Fconversation about what we think went
OL,12,Fwell, what went wrong, and how we deal
OL,13,Fwith this upcoming year."
