OL,3,CLiberal Democrats celebrate after
OL,4,Ctaking top target Stockport Council
OL,6,FLisa Smart, the MP for Hazel Grove
OL,7,Ftold ITV Granada she was overjoyed
OL,8,Fwith the result, saying: "It's already
OL,9,Fcouncil of the year, it's the best
OL,10,Fplace to live in the North West and I
OL,11,Fcouldn't be prouder of the amazing
OL,12,Fgroup of Lib Dem campaigners and
OL,13,Factivists. But I'm most happy for the
OL,14,Fpeople of Stockport."
OL,16,F"We've shown what we can do when we're
OL,17,Fin minority control, I look forward to
OL,18,Fseeing what the council can do going
OL,19,Fforward now we're in majority control."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
